		{
			"id":"058a7c11cfdf115d",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Detachment Types\n\n| Detachment Type | Directive Flavor                             |\n| --------------- | -------------------------------------------- |\n| Strike          | Scores by destroying enemy units.            |\n| Hold            | Scores by maintaining control of objectives. |\n| Capture         | Scores by taking objectives from enemies.    |\n| Claim           | Scores by board control.                     |\n| Delve           | Scores by performing actions in terrain.     |\n| Unique*         | Scores by using faction based stuff.         |\n",
			"dynamicHeight":true,
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-70,
			"y":-600,
			"width":440,
			"height":460
		},
		{
