		{
			"id":"554ab238dc4c7984",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"\n|  #  | Name                                  | Requirement                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | VP Gain | Boon |\n| :-: | ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------- | ---- |\n|  1  | Survey for Resources                  | Have a unit perform an [[Claim]] Standard Action while being fully within 9\" of the center of the battle field.                                                                                                                                                                                | 2       |      |\n|  2  | Deploy REU (Resource Extraction Unit) | A unit can deploy a [[REU]] within 3\" of this unit in No Man's Land as a standard action and until it is destroyed or you loose control of it, it generates 1VP during each Upkeep phase.                                                                                                      | Up to 4 |      |\n|  3  | Enemy Deployment Zone Action          | Have a unit perform a [[Claim]] Standard Action while being fully within the Enemy deployment zone.                                                                                                                                                                                            | 2       |      |\n|  4  | Wide Search                           | Have units perform a [[Claim]] Standard action in different parts of the board in terrain<br>- Fully within 1\" of a terrain piece in Your deployment zone 1<br>- Fully within 1\" of a terrain piece in NoMans Land 1<br>- Fully within 1\" of a terrain piece in your enemies deployment zone 2 | up to 4 |      |\n|  5  | Delayed Payout                        | In each quarter of the board a unit can deploy a single [[LTREU]] within 3\" of this unit and outside of terrain as a Full Action. For each [[LTREU]] you control at the end of the game gain 2VP up to 6VP.                                                                                    | up to 5 |      |\n|  6  | Pick one                              | Pick one above                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |         |      |\n|     |                                       |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |         |      |\n\n\n",
			"dynamicHeight":true,
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":480,
			"y":-140,
			"width":1120,
			"height":480
		},
		{
			"id":"e19457a1da451232",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Claim Detachment",
			"dynamicHeight":true,
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":1680,
			"y":-200,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"96099019ad460c02",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"\n|  #  | Name                 | Requirement                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | VP Gain | Boon |\n| :-: | -------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------- | ---- |\n|  1  | Show of Force        | Have more units from your army fully within No Man's Land than your opponent.                                                                                                                                                                   | 2       |      |\n|  2  | Behind Enemy lines   | Have 2 or more units from your army fully within your opponents deployment zone.                                                                                                                                                                | 3       |      |\n|  3  | Stolen Intel         | Your opponent places a [[Point of Interest\\|POI]] in No Man's Land 6\" away from any deployment zone.<br>If you have control of that [[Point of Interest\\|POI]] at the end of the battle round then gain 2VP and remove it from the battle field | 2       |      |\n|  4  | Engage on all fronts | Have units in the table quarters<br>- 2 Table quarters 1VP<br>- 3 Table quarters 2VP<br>- 4 Table quarters 4VP                                                                                                                                  | Up to 3 |      |\n|  5  | Take what is ours    | At the end of the battle round control one or more [[Point of Interest\\|POI]] that had an enemy unit on it at the beginning of the battle round.                                                                                                | 3VP     |      |\n|  6  | Pick one             | Pick one above                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |         |      |\n\n\n",
			"dynamicHeight":true,
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":1680,
			"y":-140,
			"width":1040,
			"height":460
		},
		{
			"id":"3c44b2b710d871c6",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"\n|  #  | Name            | Requirement                                                                                                                                             | VP Gain | Boon |\n| :-: | --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------- | ---- |\n|  1  | Killing Tally   | Destroy more models than your opponent this battle round.                                                                                               | 2       |      |\n|  2  | Destroy         | Fully destory a unit.                                                                                                                                   | 1       |      |\n|  3  | Combined Strike | Two or more units from your army performed a strike action against the same target this battle round.                                                   | 2       |      |\n|  4  | Assassinate     | Destroy a specialist.                                                                                                                                   | 2       |      |\n|  5  | Marked          | Your opponent chooses a target unit and you choose a target unit from their army. <br>- If you destroy their target 2<br>- If you destroy your target 1 | up to 3 |      |\n|  6  | Pick one        | Pick one above                                                                                                                                          |         |      |\n\n\n",
			"dynamicHeight":true,
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":480,
			"y":-580,
			"width":1040,
			"height":340
		},
		{
			"id":"a959159069449c60",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"\n|  #  | Name          | Requirement                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |\n| :-: | ------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|  1  | Elimination   | Each player scores 3VP if they destroyed 1 or more enemy units during the battle round.                                                                                                                                                                                           |\n|  2  | Terrain       | The player that does not have priority chooses 3 terrain features that are in No Man's Land those terrain features become [[Point of Interest\\|POI]] for the rest of the game. Players score 4VP for each they control at the end of each battle round.                           |\n|  3  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  4  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  5  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  6  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  7  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  8  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  9  |               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n| 10  | Resource Hunt | Deal damage to a large construct that roams around and deals damage. If defeated then another one shows up on the opposite board edge from where the last one was defeated. Players who damage the large construct during the battle round gain 1VP for every 2 damage they deal. |\n\n\n",
			"dynamicHeight":false,
